data.description: Welcome to your own home on a corner lot in a private lake community. 3 bedroom, 1 bath updated ranch on a beautiful lot. This yard is perfect for a playground, firepit, or just a peaceful outdoor relaxing space under the trees. Large outbuilding for workshop or extra storage. Updated cabinets and newer stainless steel appliances. All appliances stay, including washer & dryer. LVP throughout. Lovely light and bright bathroom. This is a unique property with access to 2 spring fed private lakes within the community for a minimal annual fee. Lakes are perfect for boats with electric motors, canoeing, kayaks, fishing, or just hanging out on the private beach with picnic area. The neighborhood makes for a good choice for first time buyers, people wanting to downsize, or an excellent rental investment. Just a few minutes to Gwinnett. Easy to get to Conyers, Covington, Loganville, & Monroe.  The location provides enough space and privacy while being very convenient to dining, entertainment, and shopping.
